'''Flitchee''' was an [[Ewok/Legends|Ewok]] fire spirit that caused mischief by kicking embers out of burning fires. "Flitchee" was a popular name given to male Ewoks,<ref name="GCG">''[[Galactic Campaign Guide]]''</ref> such as [[Flitchee/Legends|the Ewok]] who fought in the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]].<ref name="Hasbro">{{HasbroCite|set=Star Wars: Movie Heroes|pack=Ewok Pack|altlink=https://www.rebelscum.com/Ewok_Pack_2012_Star_Wars_Movie_Heroes_Hasbro.asp}}</ref>

